<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;padding-bottom:0; text-align:center;"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Buddhism_by_country" title="Buddhism by country">Buddhism by country</a></div><div class="NavContent hlist" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center;padding-top:0;">
