<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Buddhism_in_Thailand" title="Buddhism in Thailand">Thailand</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Tibetan_Buddhism" title="Tibetan Buddhism">Tibet</a></li>
