<p><figure-inline class="noviewer" typeof="mw:Image"><a href="./File:Dharma_Wheel.svg"><img resource="./File:Dharma_Wheel.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Dharma_Wheel.svg/16px-Dharma_Wheel.svg.png" data-file-width="690" data-file-height="690" data-file-type="drawing" height="16" width="16" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Dharma_Wheel.svg/32px-Dharma_Wheel.svg.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Dharma_Wheel.svg/24px-Dharma_Wheel.svg.png 1.5x"/></a></figure-inline> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Portal:Buddhism" title="Portal:Buddhism">Buddhism<span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>portal</a></p>
